Project will continue to be enhanced in future quarters



---

Programming and Computing Ethics

All code in this repository was written by the student based on concepts learned in class. No proprietary or copyrighted code was copied.

User privacy is respected by not collecting personal information and by storing all data locally. Accessibility was considered by using a simple, text-based interface that is easy to navigate.

These practices align with the principles of the Association for Computing Machinery Code of Ethics, particularly regarding responsibility, honesty, and respect for users.


